{"tid":1447351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地做得好啱，流動式癱瘓社會！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:50:22.000Z","uid":35910,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e540e7a871a85f33939adf2b28fa45f9c07582d","tid":1447351,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"自6月9日以黎，中共為左維穩已經無所不用其極，肆無忌憚<br />\n<br />\n香港人既言論自由、集會自由同遊行自由已被<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">褫奪</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今晚行動明顯再被以前急、直接、粗暴同違反更多規條法律。<br />\n<br />\n代表我地做得好啱，中共急住撲滅我地！越近九月十月就越急！<br />\n<br />\n接下來<br />\n<br />\n1）蒐集更多中共維穩惡行，大肆於國際宣揚，文宣對國際Reddit永遠唔可以漏！<br />\n<br />\n同時將721事件、爆眼少女打格相同警察冒黑衣人既文宣貼哂香港每一個角落！<br />\n<br />\n每個字都要對準政權！<br />\n<br />\n長輩圖一開始文宣用過咩招全部要繼續！<br />\n<br />\n2）唔可以有手足被捕，遊行集會要更加Be Water，時刻制訂逃生路線，留意Telegram同連登經認證頻道，勿輕信現場消息。<br />\n（呢啲頻道要小心滲透）<br />\n<br />\n同時留意現場有戴耳機既黑衣人。<br />\n<br />\n安全既地方就只有各大商場私人屋苑同徒步走出警方防線，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走出去永遠最安全</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n集會遊行造成既社會混亂效果正面既，接下來就重點<br />\n<br />\n3）經紅隧就拆撚哂車閘佢，破壞閘機。<br />\n經過每支交通燈都要噴黑佢。<br />\n去地鐵快閃緊急制<br />\n<br />\n你話驚失民意？唔驚，等上面文宣三張相貼通街，無時無刻提醒每個善忘既香港人，有良知既無可能會反對你地既做法。<br />\n<br />\n淨底既就係無良知既人，滲透教說工作由有心人負責。<br />\n<br />\n4）<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港革命必載入史書，今日證明我地一直方向正確無做錯到！關於第三點，歡迎利用你既創意去癱瘓社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBe water，要無孔不入<br />\n<br />\n今次唔可以驚，唔可以怯，唔可以俾白色恐怖得逞，要更加企出黎，唔係既話你以後準備每一日都活係白色恐怖之下。"},{"pid":"d5287f442639f93e32b4a54b8ace60e6bb947a50","tid":1447351,"uid":32719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2y1HgQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2y1HgQR.jpg&h=80717eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KEmxpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KEmxpb.jpg&h=23067af2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Bz5Y4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Bz5Y4b.jpg&h=09474ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6QwUCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6QwUCx.png&h=fe8a28fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2jm4vaT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2jm4vaT.png&h=195a48db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxsfBQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxsfBQX.jpg&h=ce495b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CodyovX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCodyovX.png&h=b7d55757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41698134b2ae68d4c02942cd84d230739d1e9673","tid":1447351,"uid":216070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"啲狗冚家剷冇人可憐"},{"pid":"fcafe8d16433fe463d37fada74478cbce2600729","tid":1447351,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"我自推十萬次，好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d07e50c9522ce67290094280a2ae776035378b5","tid":1447351,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"啱，要由經濟入手。再將經濟問題歸究番送中+貿易戰"},{"pid":"fbc13d353c27fc6dd35a13439dbfb33b0e37aada","tid":1447351,"uid":35910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"41698134b2ae68d4c02942cd84d230739d1e9673","tid":1447351,"uid":216070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"啲狗冚家剷冇人可憐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實禍真係要及家人</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3f9166780cee5d325f614f1ae8601ba4